        "topic": "",
        "payload": "{\"callback_url\":\"https://registry.hub.docker.com/u/saashup/curio.city/hook/e516e7b77b86461aa659013befa31d39/\",\"push_data\":{\"pusher\":\"saashup\",\"pushed_at\":1773402989,\"tag\":\"v0.34.0\",\"images\":[],\"media_type\":\"application/vnd.docker.container.image.v1+json\"},\"repository\":{\"status\":\"Active\",\"namespace\":\"saashup\",\"name\":\"curio.city\",\"repo_name\":\"saashup/curio.city\",\"repo_url\":\"https://hub.docker.com/r/saashup/curio.city\",\"description\":\"\",\"full_description\":\"# Curio.city — Guide\\n\\nInstance for every guide \\\\o/\\n\\n## Development\\nTo start the development server run:\\n```bash\\nbun run dev\\n```\\n\\nOpen http://localhost:3000/ with your browser to see the result.\\n\\n## E2E Tests\\n\\nWe use [Playwright](https://playwright.dev/) as E2E tests runner.\\n\\nRun the tests:\\n\\n1. Be sure your have project dependencies installed with `bun install`\\n2. Install headless browsers packages `bunx playwright install`\\n3. Start the Guide instance `bun run dev`\\n4. Exec the tests `bunx --bun playwright test tests/dom/`\\n\\n\",\"star_count\":0,\"is_private\":true,\"is_trusted\":false,\"is_official\":false,\"owner\":\"saashup\",\"date_created\":1723641910}}",
